{
  "version": "2.0.0",
  "comment": "Single source of truth for animation presets. Read by PHP (Animation_Presets), runtime JS (animations.js), and React admin. Adding a preset here = automatic exposure across all 3 layers. Each preset documents the EXACT GSAP parameters required by its skill file (gsap-core / gsap-timeline / gsap-scrolltrigger / gsap-plugins). UI controls are auto-generated from the params schema — impossible to invent a knob GSAP doesn't support.",
